  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Minecraft: Thigh High Mod</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Adds 9 different craftable Thigh High types to the game!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Includes:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Fully White</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Blue and White</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Pink and White</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Black and White</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Black and Purple</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Yellow and White</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Black and Green</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Green</span> and White</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #ff0000;\">R<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">a<span style=\"color: #ffff00;\">i<span style=\"color: #339966;\">n<span style=\"color: #00ffff;\">b<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">o<span style=\"color: #ff00ff;\">w</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Recipes</span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>White Thigh Highs (Base)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008069864004534443/unknown.png\" alt=\"White Thigh Highs are crafted with 6 White Wool\" width=\"244\" height=\"115\" /></p>\n<p>Blue and White Thigh Highs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008070159325466644/unknown.png\" alt=\"Blue and White Thigh Highs need Light Blue Dye and the White Thigh Highs\" width=\"239\" height=\"115\" /></p>\n<p>Pink and White Thigh Highs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008070359557341256/unknown.png\" alt=\"Same as the Blue and White Thigh Highs, but with Pink Dye\" width=\"242\" height=\"117\" /></p>\n<p>Black and White Thigh Highs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008070661090050098/unknown.png\" alt=\"Black Dye with Base Thigh Highs\" width=\"248\" height=\"122\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Black and Purple Thigh Highs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008070980972855396/unknown.png\" alt=\"Black and Purple Dye with the Base Thigh Highs\" width=\"239\" height=\"115\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Yellow and White Thigh Highs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008071208442536088/unknown.png\" alt=\"Yellow Dye with the Base Thigh Highs\" width=\"245\" height=\"120\" /></p>\n<p>Black and Green Thigh Highs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008071382644572211/unknown.png\" alt=\"Black and Lime Dye with Base Thigh Highs\" width=\"242\" height=\"116\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Green and White Thigh Highs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008071618284752928/unknown.png\" alt=\"Base with Lime Dye\" width=\"244\" height=\"116\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Rainbow Thigh Highs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1006929107155681314/1008071811612823603/unknown.png\" alt=\"You can actually use any dye for these\" width=\"242\" height=\"118\" /></p>\n<p>You can actually use any dye for the Rainbow Thigh Highs.</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
